<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Wildcard route is a route which allows for additional URL parameter fetching like it was possible with the first router version. You will have a possibility to define a place in a route from where all variable and value pairs will be fetched and set as action parameters.</p>

<p>Map 'news/view/*' will catch URLs like:</p>

<p>/news/view/id/3
/news/view
/news/view/show/all/sort/date</p>

